[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15843] added comparison support to 
``bench``
 command
weirdan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15842] set content_type for 
``view span``
 output
new-years-eve 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15839] refactored 
``find``
 to handle regex and non-regex searches consistently
hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15835] fixed build failure of aarch64 and armv7 musl targets
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15828] allowed specifying MSI version via env var and workflow input
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15815] updated comments of release-pkg.nu for MSI package building
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15809] bumped dev version to 0.104.2
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15808] used nushell's fork for winget-pkgs publishing
pyz4:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15834] expanded 
``polars shift``
 to allow expression inputs
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15826] added Value::Record to 
``NuExpression::can_downcast``
 logic
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15822] added 
``polars math``
 expression
cptpiepmatz:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15820] moved job errors into 
``ShellError::Job``
 variant
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15817] improved error for prefix-only path for PWD
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15812] switched to 
``ring``
 as crypto provider instead of 
``aws_lc``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15810] added 
``rustls``
 for TLS
rritik772 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15818] fixed #15813 - passing infinity to random float causes error
noahfraiture 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15804] added default http protocol when none specified
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15798] ensured block is compiled when parsing 
``source``
vivainio 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15792] optimized kv get by selecting only one row from storage db
Villa01 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15787] improved error handling for unsupported --theme in to html
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15772] handled multiple exact matches
jjflash95 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15601] fixed #15571 panic on write to source parquet file
flovilmart 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15369] implemented reedline for input
